-hydro","content":"--watch 启用热重载（实验性）"},"424":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev-66","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev#启动-hydro","content":"使用 yarn debug --port=2333 --watch 启动 Hydro，并在后台运行 yarn build:ui:dev，可以对前端源码进行实时转译，在反复修改时可节省编译时间。启动完成后，您可以在 8000 端口访问到 Hydro 实例，且前端的任何更改将即时生效。（后端热重载可能存在 bug，部分模块修改后可能仍需重启才能生效）请注意：此功能仅在启用了 @hydrooj/ui-default 插件的情况下才会生效。"},"425":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev-67","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev#启动-hydro","content":"首次启动会要求您填写数据库连接信息。请根据您数据库的安装填写（若无密码则留空）请按照下文说明创建管理员账户即可正常使用。"},"426":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev-68","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev#更新","content":"需要更新的时候进入对应仓库文件夹执行 git pull，然后重新 yarn && yarn build:ui:production 即可。"},"427":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"page","content":"命名规则","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming"},"428":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"变量命名规则"},"429":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#函数命名规则","content":"函数命名规则"},"430":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"在 Hydro 中的大部分变量有固定命名规则："},"431":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"pdoc: 题目"},"432":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"tdoc: 比赛/作业/训练"},"433":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"rdoc: 提交记录"},"434":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming#变量命名规则","content":"ddoc: 讨论"},"435":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/naming-7","page_id":"/docs/H