持","content":"如果您添加了新的语言，您还需要前往 控制面板>系统设置 中修改 Language Highlight ID 与 Monaco language modes。分别表示选择对应的语言后的高亮设置（基于 PrismJS）和 Monaco 编辑器语法规则设置。"},"681":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-44","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"修改完后请重启 Hydro 和 hydrojudge 。"},"682":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-45","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调试沙箱环境","content":"如果需要调试沙箱内的编译或者运行错误，可以使用 hydrojudge terminal 来打开评测交互终端。该终端运行于与评测环境相同的独立沙箱内。"},"683":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-46","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#清除数据缓存","content":"若需要清除评测数据缓存，可以使用 hydrojudge cache prune 清除 30 天之内未使用的测试数据，需指定天数可添加参数 --duration=x 清除 x 天数据。"},"684":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-47","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#清除数据缓存","content":"若需清除所有缓存数据，可以使用 hydrojudge cache clean 命令。"},"685":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-48","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#测试数据格式","content":"参照 测试数据格式 配置。"},"686":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-49","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"如果不调整沙箱的空间大小，当您的评测使用文件 IO 且输入输出文件较大时可能会引发错误。"},"687":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-50","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"对于 2022/8/12 前安装的用户："},"688":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-51","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"在服务器上运行下面的代码找到 hydro-sandbox 的运行目录："},"689":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-52","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"参照 沙箱文件系统挂载文档 中的自定义挂载的配置，保存配置内容到运行目录并命名为 mount.yaml。\n修改配置文件中 work dir 和 tmp dir 所对应 size 和 nr_inodes 的挂载参数至您想要的大小，保存后重启 hydro-sandbox 即可完成更改。"},"690":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-53","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"对于 2022/8/12 后安装的用户："},"691":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-54","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调整沙箱空间大小","content":"编辑 /root/.hydro/mount.yaml，修改 size 即可。"},"692":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-55","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"确认您安装了支持彩色输出的编译器；"},"693":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-56","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"在系统设置中，将 C/C++ 编译命令后加上 -fdiagnostics-color=always"},"694":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-57","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"例："},"695":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-58","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"2022/8/12 后安装的实例默认已开启无限栈空间，无需手动操作"},"696":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-59","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"在很多时候系统默认为程序提供的栈空间并不能满足我们的需求，此时我们需要手动为用户程序提供更大的栈空间。"},"697":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-60","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#开大程序运行栈空间","content":"修改 pm2 中 hydro-sandbox 的启动参数为 ulimit -s unlimited && /usr/bin/hydro-sandbox ："},"698":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-61","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#提高测评精度","content":"禁用 CPU 频率缩放与 Intel 睿频加速技术，防止 CPU 频率波动。"},"699":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-62","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#提高测评精度","content":"禁用内存地址空间随机化，以使得存在内存寻址错误的代码能够得到更多可重复的结果，可以通过在 /etc/sysctl.conf 中添加下面这行并运行 sudo sysctl -p 应用："},"700":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-63","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"在控制面板上出现内容为 You are using cgroup v2 without kernel 5.19+. This could result in inaccurate memory usage measurements. 警告时，意味着当前系统的内存消耗计量存在误差。"},"701":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-64","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"部分 Linux 设备默认使用 cgroup2，而在 5.19 版本前的内核的 cgroup2 中移除了精确计量内存消耗的接口。\n若要获得更精确的内存计量，推荐启用 cgroup v1 (您可以通过检查 /sys/fs/cgroup/memory/memory.memsw.usage_in_bytes 是否存在来验证是否当前系统是否启用了 cgroup v1 )："},"702":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-65","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"以 Ubuntu 的默认引导器 GRUB 2 为例，编辑 /etc/default/grub：\n在其中"},"703":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-66","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"后，加入 `cgroup_enable=memory swapaccount=1 systemd.unified_cgroup_hierarchy=0，变为："},"704":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-67","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存计量不准确","content":"运行以下命令更新 GRUB 2 的配置，然后重新启动。"},"705":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-68","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"在控制面板上出现内容为 The memory cgroup controller is not enabled. This could result in inaccurate memory usage measurements. 警告时，意味着当前系统并没有开启内存 cgroup 控制器。"},"706":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-69","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"部分 Linux (如 Raspbian) 并不会默认开启内存 cgroup 控制器，启用内存控制器可以获得更精确的内存限制和计量。"},"707":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-70","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"以 Raspbian 为例，编辑 /boot/firmware/cmdline.txt (如果不存在则 /boot/cmdline.txt)：\n在末尾添加（注意空格）"},"708":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-71","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#内存控制器未开启","content":"重启之后检查 /proc/cgroups 确认内存控制器 memory 已开启。"},"709":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"page","content":"插件","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins"},"710":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#附加组件列表","content":"附加组件列表"},"711":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#安装","content":"安装"},"712":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#查看已注册的插件列表","content":"查看已注册的插件列表"},"713":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#更新","content":"更新"},"714":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#卸载","content":"卸载"},"715":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","content":"Hydro 支持使用插件扩展自身所支持的功能。"},"716":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","content":"插件对站点的所有内容具有完全的访问权限，请不要启用来历不明的插件。"},"717":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#附加组件列表","content":"使用安装脚本安装时会自动安装下方加粗的插件。\n部分插件（斜体标注）需配合第三方软件使用，如仅安装不配置/不安装第三方软件会导致系统无法正常运行，详情请前往左侧插件详情查看。"},"718":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins#附加组件列表","content":"