d":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#创建评测账号","content":"完成后将配置的用户名及密码写入评测机配置文件，评测机即可连接到网页端。"},"890":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#黑名单相关","content":"用户封禁："},"891":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#黑名单相关","content":"IP/邮箱域名封禁："},"892":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#命令列表","content":"所有于 此文件夹 下的函数均可用 cli 调用。"},"893":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#命令列表","content":"这里并没有列出所有可以运行的指令，因为其中很多功能我们更推荐通过 Web 访问。"},"894":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"page","content":"数据库备份和恢复","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database"},"895":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"进入数据库"},"896":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"快速备份与恢复"},"897":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"手动备份"},"898":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动恢复备份","content":"手动恢复备份"},"899":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"非常不推荐直接操作数据库！"},"900":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"当你改动一个字段的时候，可能与其相关的部分忘记修改，改完觉得好像没什么问题，过段时间发现了一些异常，根本不会想到是你这次改数据库导致的，之后又不会修。"},"901":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"直接修改数据库后，可能没有通知主程序，缓存仍然存在，表现为修改不生效。"},"902":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"直接操作数据库的权限过大，若操作失误带来的影响通常是灾难性的。"},"903":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"在绝大部分情况下均不需要/不可以直接操作数据库。若确需要，可使用 hydrooj db 命令打开数据库 shell，也可以从 ~/.hydro/config.json 查找数据库 connection string 并使用外部工具进行连接。"},"904":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"注：MongoDB 的用户是附加在特定数据库中的，使用外部工具连接请确保使用了正确的 authSource 选项。"},"905":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"为了保证数据安全，请定期备份。"},"906":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"若您使用自动脚本安装，可使用 hydrooj backup 快捷备份数据，备份完成后会在当前目录生成备份压缩包文件，您可使用 hydrooj restore <备份文件路径> 恢复之前备份的数据。"},"907":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"可使用 MongoDB 自带的 mongodump 进行数据库备份。并将 /data/file 文件夹备份即可。"},"908":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"对于数据库，请请不要在数据库运行时直接拷贝数据库文件夹。请每次备份后检查生成的备份文件的大小和内容，确保备份成功。请不要把备份数据和 Hydro 系统放在同一台机器上，这样数据丢失的风险仍然较高。"},"909":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动恢复备份","content":"使用 MongoDB 自带的 mongorestore 导入备份的数据库文件，并还原 /data/file 目录文件。如果只是想不同机器之间迁移部署，只需要在停止 Hydro 和 MongoDB 服务后将相关文件夹（通常为 /data/db 与 /data/file 与 /root/.hydro/config.json ）复制即可。"},"910":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"page","content":"前端修改","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify"},"911":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"修改页面翻译或是添加新语言："},"912":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"修改页面模板："},"913":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"此指南将教您修改前端文件。"},"914":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"如果您正在使用开发者模式，请直接修改 packages/ui-default/templates 下的文件。"},"915":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"如果您使用安装脚本部署："},"916":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"请先使用 hydrooj addon create 创建一个本地插件（如果之前没有做过的话）。"},"917":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"修改翻译：在 zh.yaml 内搜索您需要修改的翻译内容，并将 其所在行而非整个文件 修改后添加至 ~/addon/locales/zh.yaml 。"},"918":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"添加语言：可参照 zh.yaml 格式创建一个新文件。欢迎社区参与多国化翻译工作。"},"919":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"通常的，在您访问的 url 前加上 view-source:（如 view-source:https://hydro.ac 即可查看页面源代码，在第二行的 <html data-page=\"xxx\"> 中 data-page 值即为页面名（首页例外，为 main.html）。\n在 默认 templates 中找到对应文件，将文件的全部内容 复制到 ~/addon/templates/ 文件夹下后进行修改即可。"},"920":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"特别的，创建题目时的默认模板位于 partials/problem_default.md，创建训练计划时的默认模板位于 partials/training_default.json，修改方式同上。"},"921":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"以上所有更改均会在重启 Hydro 后生效。"},"922":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"page","content":"导入用户","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user"},"923":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"目前支持 csv 格式（用 , 分隔）或 Excel 格式（用 TAB 分隔） 导入用户数据, 数据既可以用文本编辑器创建，也可以用 Excel 等软件来辅助创建。"},"924":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"每行最少三列，最多五列，分别为: 邮箱，用户名，密码，显示名，用户信息。（显示名和用户信息为可选）请使用 UTF-8 编码，否则中文可能会乱码。如果使用 CSV 格式（逗号分隔），则用户信息列不可用。"},"925":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"可以在粘贴后点击预览验证复制入的数据的有效性"},"926":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"这将创建三个用户："},"927":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user1 密码为 password1 , 邮箱 foo@undefined.moe；"},"928":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user2 密码为 password2 ，邮箱 bar@undefined.moe，显示名为 temp；"},"929":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user3 密码为 password3，邮箱 test@undefined.moe，显示名为 test，学校为 Hydro School，学号为 123，该用户将会被分配至当前域的 class1 小组内；"},"930":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"用户创建后无法删除，请谨慎操作"},"931":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"page","content":"维护","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain"},"932":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2","content":"PM2"},"933":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"进程名称"},"934":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"PM2 基本指令"},"935":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#更新","content":"更新"},"936":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#查看已安装版本","content":"查看已安装版本"},"937":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#清除缓存","content":"清除缓存"},"938":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2","content":"使用一键安装脚本安装的 Hydro 使用 PM2 对进程进行管理。"},"939":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"可以通过下面的指令查看当前 PM2 正在管理的所有进程。"},"940":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"一键安装脚本默认会创建下面几个进程："},"941":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"hydrooj： Hydro 主进程"},"942":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"hydro-sandbox： Hydro 评测沙箱"},"943":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"mongodb： MongoDB 数据库"},"944":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"caddy： 反向代理"},"945":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"后文的指令中将用 <name> 替代此处的进程名称，用 <id> 替代进程 ID（进程 ID 可通过 pm2 ls 查看）。（尖括号同样需要替换）"},"946":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"在部分环境（常见于 lxc 容器或是精简版系统）下，服务器重启后 Hydro 可能不能正常自启动，这时请使用 pm2 resurrect 手动载入进程列表。"},"947":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"如果手动修改进程列表且已经覆盖掉保存的原列表，请使用 pm2 stop all && pm2 del all 清空所有进程之后重新运行安装脚本。原有数据不会丢失。"},"948":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"Hydro 主进程同样支持多进程启动，但在中低端服务器（不超过4核）中没有必要使用多进程启动 Hydro，会降低性能且成倍提高内存占用。"},"949":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#更新","content":"Hydro 系统会不定期发布更新，可以使用下面的命令获取更新。"},"950":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#更新","content":"无特殊情况请 不要更新PM2 ！此操作可能导致进程列表丢失！"},"951":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","type":"page","content":"现场赛指南","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest"},"952":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","content":"参照 XCPC-Tools"},"953":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"page","content":"复制题目","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem"},"954":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#操作流程","content":"操作流程"},"955":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#限制","content":"限制"},"956":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","content":"复制题目可以帮助用户将任何有权提交的题目复制到有权创建题目的域中以在比赛/作业/训练计划中使用这些题目。"},"957":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#操作流程","content":"进入需要复制的题目页面或是题目列表页面。"},"958":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#操作流程","content":"点击右侧栏底部的“复制”按钮或是多选题目后点击右侧复制题目按钮。"},"959":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#操作流程","content":"在弹出的窗口中输入需要复制到的域的 ID。"},"960":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#操作流程","content":"点击“确定”后将自动跳转到复制后的题目连接。"},"961":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#限制","content":"不允许查看/修改复制后的题目的测试数据。"},"962":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#限制","content":"不能复制一个复制来的题目。"},"963":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem#限制","content":"部分题目可能不允许复制。这遵循 域设置>编辑域资料 中的管理员设定。"},"964":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"page","content":"域","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain"},"965":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#简介","content":"简介"},"966":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"创建域"},"967":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#初始化讨论节点","content":"初始化讨论节点"},"968":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#访问控制","content":"访问控制"},"969":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"Hydro v5"},"970":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v4","content":"Hydro v4"},"971":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建比赛作业","content":"创建比赛/作业"},"972":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"创建训练"},"973":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#简介","content":"域功能类似团队，允许在一套系统中创建多个环境（如不同班级，或是不同功能，等等）用户可以创建多个域。（需要用户有 PRIV_CREATE_DOMAIN 权限，默认仅开放给管理员账户）。\n域间数据完全独立，仅用户信息相通（注册账户后，在该实例的所有域中均有效）。"},"974":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"登录账号后，在“我的”选项卡中找到“我的域”，并点击“创建域”，填入以下信息："},"975":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"ID： 每个域有一个唯一的 ID，将会在域 URL 中体现。创建后无法修改。"},"976":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"名称： 域的名字，创建后可以更改。"},"977":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"公告： 域主页上显示的公告，创建后可以更改。"},"978":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"avatar： 域头像，与用户头像同理，可以使用 gravatar:email 或 qq:id 或 github:name 或 url:link 的格式添加。将会在“我的域”界面内显示。"},"979":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"创建域后，您将在此域中拥有管理员权限，可以在域内进行添加题目/创建比赛等操作。"},"980":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#初始化讨论节点","content":"您可以在“管理域”选项卡中点击“初始化讨论节点”按钮初始化讨论节点。"},"981":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"Hydro v5 开始，未登录的用户和未加入域的用户在域内默认 guest 权限，加入域的用户默认使用 default 权限。您可以在加域管理中设置 允许用户自助加入域，分配 default 权限。以获得和 v4 相同的权限效果。在 v5 中，只有加域用户会显示在域排行榜中。域管理员修改特定用户的权限为除 default 或 guest 之外的权限后，该用户加入域时将可以绕过其他条件要求，并在加入域时自动应用分配的角色。将用户的权限显式设置为 guest 可以防止用户使用自助加域功能加入域。加域后可以主动退出或被管理员踢出域，此时用户权限组还原为 guest，直至再次加入域。只有已经加入的域会在 “我的域” 中显示。用户注册后会自动加入 system 域，并不可主动退出。"},"982":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"在 Hydro v4 至 Hydro v5 的升级过程中，将执行以下操作："},"983":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"标记所有现有用户为已加入"},"984":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"将未设置加域条件与设置为没有用户可以自助加入的域设置为允许所有用户自助加入，权限分配为 default"},"985":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v4","content":"未登录用户将默认使用 guest 权限，登录用户将默认使用 default 权限。（所以将登陆用户设为 default 权限后并不会显示在“管理用户”页内，这也表示所有用户默认不会出现在管理列表中）所以将一个用户的权限设为 default 和将用户移出该域是等价的。"},"986":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v4","content":"对于不在列表中的用户，点击右上角“添加用户”，在左侧选中用户，右侧选择权限组，再点击“确定”即可。"},"987":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建比赛作业","content":"若您想要创建比赛/作业，您可以在“比赛”或“作业”选项卡中，在页面右侧找到“创建”按钮，\n题目一栏支持根据题目ID或是题目名自动筛选。设置完后可点击“创建”按钮创建比赛（描述这类的框不知道写啥就随便填，不能留空）。"},"988":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建比赛作业","content":"若因为删除作业/比赛内题目导致无法打开，可以通过 /contest/<id>/edit 或 /homework/<id>/edit（即在无法打开的页面页面后加上 /edit）直接访问编辑页并修正。"},"989":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"若您想要创建训练，您可以在“训练” 项卡中点击“新建训练计划”，填写以下信息："},"990":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"标题：该训练的标题；"},"991":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"简介：该训练的简介，会与标题同时显示在列表页面中；"},"992":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hyd