{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#认领作业","content":"认领作业"},"1006":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"Hydro 中题目的难度，根据递交数、通过率以及每个递交的递交时间和评测结果，通过算法计算得出。"},"1007":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"一般地，难度的数值越大，该题目越难。"},"1008":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"新题目的难度可能不准确；在题目获得大量递交之后，难度才会变得较为准确。"},"1009":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"越早递交评测的用户代码的评测结果对题目难度影响越大。"},"1010":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"题目的难度由算法计算得出，有可能出现不准确的结果。"},"1011":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#参与比赛","content":"您可以在比赛的详细界面内点击“参与比赛”按钮进行参与。\n比赛过程中“成绩表”会根据比赛规则显示排名。\n在比赛截止之后，您仍然可以订正其中的题目，但“成绩表”将停止更新。"},"1012":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"若您想发布一个讨论，请先进入一个讨论节点，之后点击“创建一个讨论”按钮并填写："},"1013":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"标题；"},"1014":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"内容；"},"1015":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"是否高亮：若选择后，该贴的左边将有醒目的红色线条（需要“高亮讨论”权限）；"},"1016":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"Pin：该讨论是否置顶（需要“置顶讨论”权限）。"},"1017":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"之后点击“创建”按钮进行发布。"},"1018":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#认领作业","content":"您可以在作业的详情页面中，点击“认领作业”。在作业开始之前，您无法查看作业中的题目。在作业持续时间内，您与他人的做题情况会被实时统计在“成绩表”内。在作业进入延期阶段后，您仍然可以提交题目，但成绩表内的分数将根据延期扣分规则按百分比折算。在作业截止之后，您仍然可以订正其中的题目，但“成绩表”将停止更新。"},"1019":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"page","content":"权限系统","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission"},"1020":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"Privilege"},"1021":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"Permission"},"1022":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"角色"},"1023":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#加入域","content":"加入域"},"1024":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v5","content":"Hydro v5"},"1025":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v4","content":"Hydro v4"},"1026":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","content":"Hydro 的权限系统使用双层结构，分别为 Privilege (PRIV) 和 Permission (PERM)。权限在系统内部使用位运算表示，具体的定义与数值可以查看 源代码 。"},"1027":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"Privilege 是用户在整套系统内拥有的权限，在所有域均生效。如创建用户，编辑系统设置，创建域，查看域等等。"},"1028":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"特别地，PRIV.PRIV_USER_PROFILE 控制一个账号是否能够作为普通账号登录。若不具有此权限，该账号将无法登录（被封禁）。"},"1029":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"常见需求："},"1030":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"若不想让普通用户上传文件 可以关闭default角色的 PRIV_CREATE_FILE 权限"},"1031":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"若需要关闭站内消息 可以关闭对应的 PRIV_SEND_MESSAGE 权限"},"1032":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"Permission 是用户在单个域内拥有的权限，如创建题目/比赛，发布/删除讨论等等。"},"1033":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"如果 PERM.PERM_VIEW 被禁用，则该用户无法查看此域。"},"1034":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"通常我们需要给特定的一组用户分配相同的权限。在用户量较多的时候这会非常混乱难以管理，为此我们设计了【角色】，便于批量操作与管理。角色是针对域内权限（PERM）的。在系统内置了三个角色："},"1035":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"guest （对未登录用户生效，含已封禁用户）"},"1036":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"default （对所有未指定角色的用户生效，包括未加入域的用户）"},"1037":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"root （拥有所有权限）"},"1038":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"通常情况下，如果需要对域做特殊的权限控制，应当新建一个用户组（例如 member）并将选定用户加入该用户组。将角色移出域和将用户的角色设置为 default 是等价的。若有需要，您也可以创建 teacher, admin 等其他角色。考虑到系统中的用户可能非常多（数万甚至数十万），在用户列表中仅会显示权限不为 default 的用户。"},"1039":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v5","content":"见 域 章节中的说明。"},"1040":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v4","content":"加入域的过程实际上是 用户通过某种方式自助将自己的权限组由 default 变更到另一权限组（如member） 的过程。因此在入域申请链接的权限组中选择 guest 和 default 是没有意义的。"},"1041":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"page","content":"Hydro常见题型的制做心得","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create"},"1042":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"零. hydro题目存储格式"},"1043":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#一-制做最简单的oj题目","content":"一 制做最简单的OJ题目"},"1044":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#二函数交互型题目","content":"二、函数交互型题目"},"1045":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#三半对拍-自己指定评测程序并修改测试输出格式","content":"三,半对拍-自己指定评测程序并修改测试输出格式"},"1046":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#四-全自动对拍题","content":"四. 全自动对拍题"},"1047":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#五文件读写测试","content":"五.文件读写测试"},"1048":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#六子任务测试","content":"六,子任务测试."},"1049":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#七客观题制做","content":"七,客观题制做"},"1050":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#八小结","content":"八.小结"},"1051":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"作者: laomaiqq: 29985091网址: http://82.157.98.222:8888/日期: 2022/03/16"},"1052":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"本文为作者使用hydro时的实验记录，希望对大家有帮助.包括如下内容"},"1053":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"零. hydro题目存储格式一. 制做最简单的oj题二. 含有自定义头文件的oj题，即函数交互式的题目三. 半自动对拍的oj题，即不需要录入预期输出的题四. 完全对拍题，即不需要录入输入数据和输出数据的题五. 指定输入文件和输出文件六. 多个子任务七. 客观题，即制做有标准答案的填空和选择题."},"1054":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"如果想在本地建立好题目，然后批量上传的话. 下面的格式应该对你有帮助每个题目应自占一个目录，目录名为题目编号比如1 ，2，3，4等等.每个题目目录下一般有下面的元素：problem_zh.md 这个文件是就是题目的内容，即题目的描述，是一个markdown格式的文档.probelm.yaml 文件.这个是题目的配置信息. 比如标题和标签等。testdata 子目录，对应网站里的测试数据部分里的文件，里面至少有一个config.yaml文件 用来说明测试的类型.具体内容见后面的例子如果题目有测试用例，则每个用例至少要提供一个in文件和一个输出文件(但有些测试类型不用，详情见后)additional_file子目录用来存放给做题者用的额外文件，比如头文件，图片，pdf文档等，在题目的 markdown 文档中可以用下面的格式为这些文件提供下载链接：提示文字"},"1055":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"下面为手工录入各种题型的步骤，即在网站登录后点创建题目之后的操作.如下图所示"},"1056":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydr